videos.description: Braxton Beverly caps off the fast break with a behind-the-back pass that results in an and-1 layup for North Carolina State's Torin Dorn.
videos.headline: Beverly goes behind the back to find Dorn

videos.description: Trey McGowens and Xavier Johnson finish nicely on back-to-back fast breaks for Pittsburgh to extend its lead over North Carolina State.
videos.headline: Pittsburgh capitalizes on back-to-back fast breaks
